#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Features</title>"
msgstr "<title>Funkcije</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: features.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Features</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Funkcije</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most important features and improvements are highlighted here, it would "
"make this list too long if we were to include <emphasis>all</emphasis> the "
"features and improvements. You will discover even more features in this "
"documentation and in the <ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/krusader?"
"path=ChangeLog\"><filename>ChangeLog</filename></ulink> and <ulink url="
"\"https://commits.kde.org/krusader?path=NEWS\"><filename>NEWS</filename></"
"ulink> files."
msgstr ""
"Tu so poudarjene najpomembnejše funkcije in izboljšave. Ta seznam bi bil "
"predolg, če bi vključili <emphasis>vse</emphasis> funkcije in izboljšave. Še "
"več funkcij boste odkrili v tej dokumentaciji in v <ulink url=\"https://"
"commits.kde.org/krusader?path=ChangeLog\"><filename>ChangeLog</filename></"
"ulink> in <ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/krusader?path=NEWS"
"\"><filename>NOVICE</filename></ulink> datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml\">Orthodox File "
"Manager (OFM)</ulink> features"
msgstr ""
"Funkcije <ulink url=\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml"
"\">ortodoksnega upravitelja datotek (OFM)</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two powerful and easy to use <link linkend=\"panels\">OFM panels</link>."
msgstr ""
"Dve zmogljivi in ​​enostavni za uporabo <link linkend=\"panels\">plošče OFM</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmdline\">Command Line</link> and optional <link linkend="
"\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> below."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"cmdline\">Ukazna vrstica</link> in izbirni <link linkend="
"\"termemu\">terminalni emulator</link> spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Strong <link linkend=\"keyboard-commands\">keyboard</link> orientation and "
"the ability to perform all functions without the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Močna orientacija <link linkend=\"keyboard-commands\">tipkovnice</link> in "
"zmožnost izvajanja vseh funkcij brez miške."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Context-dependent invocation of scripts and programs &eg; mouse click/"
"&Enter; (execute or open with the associated application), <keycap>F3</"
"keycap> (view) and <keycap>F4</keycap> (edit)."
msgstr ""
"Kontekstno odvisen priklic skriptov in programov &eg; klik miške/&Enter; "
"(izvedba ali odpiranje s povezano aplikacijo), <keycap>F3</keycap> (ogled) "
"in <keycap>F4</keycap> (urejanje)."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">User Menu</link>, create your own customized "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">Uporabniški meni</link>, ustvarite svoj meni "
"po meri."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"History &eg; <link linkend=\"folderhistory\">Folder History</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"popular-urls\">Popular &URL;s</link>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Zgodovina &eg; <link linkend=\"folderhistory\">Zgodovina map</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"popular-urls\">Priljubljeni &URL;-ji</link> &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"vfs\">Virtual file systems (VFS)</link> &eg; for <link "
"linkend=\"remote-connections\">Remote Connections</link>, <link linkend="
"\"archives\">archives</link>, search results, synchronizer."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"vfs\">Navidezni datotečni sistemi (VFS)</link> &eg; za <link "
"linkend=\"remote-connections\">Oddaljene povezave</link>, <link linkend="
"\"archives\">arhivi</link>, rezultati iskanja, sinhronizator."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Powerful internal <link linkend=\"krviewer\">viewer and editor</link> via "
"kparts supporting almost every file format."
msgstr ""
"Zmogljiv notranji <link linkend=\"krviewer\">pregledovalnik in urejevalnik</"
"link> prek kparts, ki podpira skoraj vse oblike datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Advanced Search module</link>: searching in "
"archives and search content on remote file systems."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Modul za napredno iskanje</link>: iskanje v "
"arhivih in iskanje po vsebini v oddaljenih datotečnih sistemih."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several Panel view modes via the <link linkend=\"sidebar\">Sidebar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Več načinov pogleda plošče prek <link linkend=\"sidebar\">stranske vrstice</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; tools"
msgstr "&krusader; orodja"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Remote Connections</link>: &FTP;/SAMBA "
"with SFTP/SCP support via KIO Slaves"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Oddaljene povezave</link>: &FTP;/SAMBA "
"s podporo SFTP/SCP prek podrejenih KIO"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"locate\">Locate</link> &GUI; frontend"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"locate\">Poišči</link> &GUI; čelni del"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize Folders"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj mape"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount-Manager"
msgstr "Mount-Manager"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disk Usage"
msgstr "Uporaba diska"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Root mode"
msgstr "Korenski način"

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; features"
msgstr "&krusader; Lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Archive Handling: browsing, unpack, pack, testing. Supported <link linkend="
"\"archives\">archives</link>: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, "
"rpm, tar, zip and 7-zip."
msgstr ""
"Ravnanje z arhivom: brskanje, razpakiranje, pakiranje, testiranje. Podprti "
"<link linkend=\"archives\">arhivi</link>: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, "
"lha, rar, rpm, tar, zip in 7-zip."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"checksum\">Checksum Creation and Verification</link> "
"mechanism that supports md5, sha1, sha256, sha224, sha256, sha384, sha512, "
"tiger, whirlpool, cfv, and crc."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"checksum\">Ustvarjanje in preverjanje kontrolne vsote</link> "
"mehanizem, ki podpira md5, sha1, sha256, sha224, sha256, sha384, sha512, "
"tiger, whirlpool, cfv in crc."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"calculate\">Calculate occupied space</link> of files and "
"folders, archives and remote filesystems."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"calculate\">Izračunaj zaseden prostor</link> datotek in map, "
"arhivov in oddaljenih datotečnih sistemov."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-dir\">Directory comparison</link> and <link linkend="
"\"view-menu\">filtering</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-dir\">Primerjava imenikov</link> in <link linkend="
"\"view-menu\">filtriranje</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-content\">Compare files by content</link> via "
"external diff programs like &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/"
"applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</application></ulink> "
"or <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/\"><application>xxdiff</"
"application></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-content\">Primerjaj datoteke po vsebini</link> prek "
"zunanjih programov za razlikovanje, kot je &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.kde.org/applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</"
"application></ulink> ali <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/"
"\"><application>xxdiff</application></ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"multi_rename\">Rename</link> files and folders via <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/utilities/krename/"
"\"><application>KRename</application></ulink>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"multi_rename\">Preimenuj</link> datoteke in mape prek <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/utilities/krename/"
"\"><application>KRename</application></ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Completely supports drag'n'drop: drag from &konqueror; straight into a "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> file, from &krusader;'s panel "
"into the trash bin, the desktop or into &konqueror;"
msgstr ""
"Popolnoma podpira povleci in spusti: povleci iz &konqueror; naravnost v "
"datoteko <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal>, s plošče &krusader; "
"v smetnjak, namizje ali v &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Preserve date</link> for local targets at "
"copy/move operations."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Ohrani datum</link> za lokalne cilje pri "
"operacijah kopiranja/premikanja."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>F9</keycap> opens a <link linkend=\"tools-menu\">Terminal Window</"
"link> in the current folder."
msgstr ""
"<keycap>F9</keycap> odpre <link linkend=\"tools-menu\">terminalsko okno</"
"link> v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Easy editing of <link linkend=\"file-menu\">file permissions</link> and "
"ownership and <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-view\">Numeric Permissions</link>."
msgstr ""
"Enostavno urejanje <link linkend=\"file-menu\">dovoljenj za datoteke</link> "
"in lastništva ter  <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-view\">številskih dovoljenj</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Selection filters</link> used in &eg; "
"Synchronizer and KruSearcher."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Izbirni filtri</link>, uporabljeni v &eg; "
"Sinhronizator in KruSearcher."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jump-Back"
msgstr "Skok nazaj"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"konfig-general\"> &MIME; type-aware</link>."
msgstr "<link linkend=\"konfig-general\"> &MIME; zavedajoč se tipa</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Tabbed panels</link> and <link linkend="
"\"krviewer\">Tabbed Editor/Viewer</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Plošča z zavihki</link> in <link linkend="
"\"krviewer\">Urejevalnik/pregledovalnik z zavihki</link>."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick search, select and filter"
msgstr "Hitro iskanje, izbira in filtriranje"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "File splitter"
msgstr "Razdelilnik datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse Gestures"
msgstr "Poteze miške"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">Quick Navigation</link> in the Location Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">Hitra navigacija</link> v orodni vrstici "
"lokacije."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "WhatsThis Help function in favour of tooltips where reasonable."
msgstr "Pomoč WhatsThis deluje v korist namigov orodij, kjer je smiselno."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sync-browsing"
msgstr "Sinhroniziranje brskanja"

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customize &krusader; to your own needs"
msgstr "Prilagodite &krusader; za lastne potrebe"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\"> Konfigurator</link> &krusader;'s "
"configuration center."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\"> Konfigurator</link> Konfiguracijski center "
"&krusader;."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Main Toolbar</link>, <link linkend="
"\"actions_toolbar\">Actions Toolbar</link> for user actions and bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Glavna orodna vrstica</link>, <link linkend="
"\"actions_toolbar\">Orodna vrstica dejanj</link> za uporabniška dejanja in "
"zaznamke."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key-bindings"
msgstr "Vezave tipk"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Barve"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panel profiles"
msgstr "Profili plošč"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark-Manager"
msgstr "Upravitelj zaznamkov"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selection Modes"
msgstr "Načini izbire"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many more features can be <link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">configured</link> "
"the way you like."
msgstr ""
"Veliko več funkcij je mogoče <link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">konfigurirati</"
"link> po želji."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; Extensions"
msgstr "&krusader; Razširitve"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "UserActions"
msgstr "Dejanja uporabnika"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Profiles"
msgstr "Barvni profili"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key-binding Profiles"
msgstr "Profili za vezavo tipk"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download and upload your favourite &krusader; extensions at <ulink url="
"\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Prenesite in naložite svoj najljubši &krusader; razširitve na <ulink url="
"\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New features in the &krusader;-1.80.0 <quote>Final 3rd Stone</quote> release"
msgstr ""
"Nove funkcije v izdaji &krusader;-1.80.0 <quote>Final 3rd Stone</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive improvements"
msgstr "Izboljšave arhiva"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Password support</link> for: arj, ace, rar and "
"zip. Passwords can be stored in <application>Kwallet</application>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Podpora za geslo</link> za: arj, ace, rar in zip. "
"Gesla lahko shranite v <application>Kwallet</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">7-zip support</link>, by external applications "
"<application>7z</application> and <application>7za</application>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Podpora za 7-zip</link>, s strani zunanjih "
"aplikacij <application>7z</application> in <application>7za</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Auto-detection support</link>, allowing you to "
"open <quote>hidden archives</quote> (&eg; <trademark class=\"registered"
"\">OpenOffice</trademark> documents)."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Podpora za samodejno zaznavanje</link>, ki vam "
"omogoča odpiranje <quote>skritih arhivov</quote> (&eg; dokumentov <trademark "
"class=\"registered\">OpenOffice</trademark>)."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Packing/unpacking is now in the background."
msgstr "Pakiranje/razpakiranje je zdaj v ozadju."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "Brief View"
msgstr "Kratek pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many improvements of the <link linkend=\"useractions\">UserActions</link> "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Veliko izboljšav sistema <link linkend=\"useractions\">UserActions</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Countless usability enhancements, especially in Konfigurator and the heavily "
"reordered menubar."
msgstr ""
"Neštete izboljšave uporabnosti, zlasti v Konfiguratorju in močno preurejeni "
"menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Media button"
msgstr "Gumb za medije"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy/Move: <link linkend=\"copying\">preserve all attributes</link> (time, "
"owner, group)."
msgstr ""
"Kopiraj/premakni: <link linkend=\"copying\">ohrani vse atribute</link> (čas, "
"lastnik, skupina)."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-color\">Dim the colors of the inactive panel</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-color\">Zatemnite barve neaktivne plošče</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Renaming a filename without extension, single instance mode, start to system "
"tray, check this out in <link linkend=\"konfigurator\">Konfigurator</link>"
msgstr ""
"Preimenovanje datoteke brez končnice, način enega primerka, zagon v "
"sistemski vrstici, preverite to v <link linkend=\"konfigurator"
"\">Konfiguratorju</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configurable <link linkend=\"list_panel\">Atomic extensions</link>, so that "
"extensions like <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> are shown as "
"one part in the <guilabel>Ext Column</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavljive <link linkend=\"list_panel\">Atomic razširitve</link>, tako da "
"so razširitve, kot je <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal>, "
"prikazane kot en del v <guilabel>stolpcu Ext</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context menu for bookmarks and enable/disable special bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"Kontekstni meni za zaznamke in omogočanje/onemogočanje posebnih zaznamkov."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restyled <link linkend=\"menu-commands\">MenuBar</link>"
msgstr "Prenovljeno <link linkend=\"menu-commands\">Menijska vrstica</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> enhancements bringing new "
"functions, new usages and new look."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"termemu\">Izboljšave terminalskega emulatorja</link> "
"prinašajo nove funkcije, nove uporabe in nov videz."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer</link> enhancements and parallel "
"threads for slow &FTP; servers."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Sinhronizator</link> izboljšave in vzporedne "
"niti za počasen &FTP; strežniki."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">Single instance mode</link>, <link linkend="
"\"konfig-startup\">start to system tray</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">Način enega primerka</link>, <link linkend="
"\"konfig-startup\">zagon v sistemski vrstici</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context menu for permanent bookmarks."
msgstr "Kontekstni meni za trajne zaznamke."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Full support for <link linkend=\"acl\">ACL permissions</link>, like "
"properties, preserve attributes, synchronizer and other."
msgstr ""
"Popolna podpora za <link linkend=\"acl\">dovoljenja ACL</link>, kot so "
"lastnosti, ohranitev atributov, sinhronizator in drugo."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searcher-results, Locate-results, Synchronizer-results: support for dragging "
"items and copy to clipboard (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Searcher-results, Locate-results, Synchronizer-results: podpora za vlečenje "
